quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  7,88,"Abaholi balabo (Bantu) abaqhoshayo phakathi kwabantu bakhe bathi, “ngempela sizokugxosha Oh Shu’aib kanye nalabo abakholwayo! Kanye nawe edolobheni lethu noma nibuyele enkolweni yethu” (uShu’aib waphendula) wathi, “noma ngabe singayithandi na”"
  7,89,"Kuyobe siqambele uMvelinqangi amanga uma sibuyele enkolweni yenu emva kokuthi esesisindisile uMvelinqangi kuyona, futhi akusikhona okwethu ukuthi siphindele kuyona ngaphandle uma ethanda uMvelinqangi iNkosi yethu. Inkosi yethu ingamele zonke izinto ngolwazi (lwayo) sithembele kuMvelinqangi (kuyena kuphela) Nkosi yethu hlulela phakathi kwethu naphakathi kwabantu bethu ngeqiniso futhi wena ungongcono kunabanye abehluleli"
  7,90,"Abaholi balabo ababengakholwa phakathi kwabantu bakhe bathi, “uma nilandela uShu’aib ngempela nina ningabalahlekileyo”"
  7,91,Ngakho-ke bathathwa ukuzamazama komhlaba basala (befile) ezindlini zabo bebhumbuluzile
  7,92,"Labo abangamkholwanga (abamphika) uShu’aib kwaba sengathi abakaze bahlale lapho (ezindlini zabo), labo ababephika uShu’aib bona babengabalahlekelweyo"
  7,93,"Ngakho-ke (uShu’ab) waqhelelana nabo futhi wathi “Oh Bantu bami! Ngiwudlulisele kunina umyalezo weNkosi yami futhi nganeluleka, ngakho-ke ngingabazwela kanjani ubuhlungu abantu abangakholwayo na”"
  7,94,Futhi asizange sithumele umphrofethi edolobheni ngaphandle kokuthi sabamba abantu balo (idolobha) ngenhlupheko nobunzima mhlawumbe ukuze bazithobe
  7,95,"Sabe sesishintsha esikhundleni sokubi ngokuhle kwaze kwaba bayanda futhi bathi, “obaba bethu bathintwa ubunzima nenjabulo ngakho-ke sabathatha ngokuzamayo ngesikhathi benganakile"
  7,96,Futhi uma abantu bamadolobha babekholiwe futhi benza ubuqotho ngempela sasizobavulela izibusiso ezivela ezulwini nasemhlabeni kepha banqaba ngakho-ke sabathatha ngenxa yalokho ababekuzuza (ababekwenza)
  7,97,Kungabe bazizwa bephephile yini abantu basemadolobheni maqondana nokuthi kuze kubona isijeziso sethu ebusuku ngesikhathi bona belele na
  7,98,Noma ngakube bazizwa bephephile yini abantu basemadolobheni maqondana nokuthi kuze kubona isijeziso sethu ekuseni ngesikhathi bona bedlala na
  7,99,"Ngakube bazizwa bephephile ecebweni likaMvelinqangi, kepha akukho namunye ophephile ecebweni likaMvelinqangi ngaphandle kwabantu abalahlekelweyo"
  7,100,Ngakube akucacile yini kulabo (bantu) abathatha izwe ukuba libe yifa emva kwabantu balo na? Ukube sasithanda sasizobajezisa ngenxa yezono zabo futhi safaka isisicilelo ezinhliziyweni zabo ukuze bangezwa
  7,101,"Lawo madolobha, sikutshena ezinye zezindaba zawo futhi ngempela zafika kubona izithunywa zabo nobufakazi obucacile kepha abazange bakholelwe kulokho ababekuphika ngaphambilini, kanjalo-ke uyazisicilela uMvelinqangi izinhliziyo zabangakholwa"
  7,102,Futhi asizange sibatholele abaningi kubona isivumelwano kepha sathola iningi labo lingabephuli bomthetho (lingamhloniphi uMvelinqangi)
  7,103,"Sabe sesithumela emva kwabo uMose nezimpawu zethu kuFaro nabaholi bakhe ngakho-ke benza okungalungile ngazo (baziphika), bheka ukuthi sasinjani isiphetho sabantu ababenza ukona"
  7,104,"Futhi uMose wathi, “Oh Faro! Ngempela mina ngiyisithunywa esivela eNkosini yemihlaba”"
  7,105,"Okuyiqiniso ukuthi ngingasho lutho ngoMvelinqangi ngaphandle kweqiniso, ngize kunina nezimpawu ezicacile ezivela eNkosini yenu ngakho-ke bathumele kanye nami abantwana bakwa-Israyeli"
  7,106,"(UFaro) wathi, “uma uze nophawu ngakho-ke luveze uma ungomunye wabaneqiniso”"
  7,107,Ngakho-ke (uMose) waphonsa induku yakhe kwaba yilapho yona iphenduka inyoka ecacile”
  7,108,Futhi wakhipha isandla sakhe kwaba yilapho sona siphenduka sibamhlophe kwabasibonayo
  7,109,"Abaholi ebantwini bakaFaro bathi, “ngempela lona ngumlumbi onolwazi (olunzulu)”"
  7,110,"(Ufaro) wathi, “ufuna ukunikhipha ezweni lenu ngakho-ke nicabanga ukuthi kwenziwe njani”"
  7,111,"(Abaholi baFaro) bathi, “mulibazise (uMose) nomfowabo bese uthumela izigijimi emadolobheni ukuyoqoqa (abalumbi)”"
  7,112,Ukuthi (izigijimi) zize kuwena nabo bonke abalumbi abanolwazi olunzulu
  7,113,"Futhi abalumbi bafika kuFaro bathi, “Ngempela kufanele sithole umvuzo uma kungukuthi thina singabanqobi”"
  7,114,"Wathi, “yebo futhi ngempela nina nizoba ngabanye balabo abasondelene (nami)”"
  7,115,Bathi (abalumbi baFaro) “Oh Mose! Uzophonsa (kuqala) noma thina sibe ngabaphonsayo”
  7,116,"(UMose) wathi, “phonsani, ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sebephonsa balumba amehlo abantu futhi babethusa futhi baveza umlingo omkhulu”"